      • downloadBatch

        public DownloadBatchOutput downloadBatch(DownloadBatchInput input)
        Downloads a batch for the user to index. It receives an object that encapsulates user's ID,and password, and it also has a project ID. If it succeeds it sends the following information. image ID, project ID, field ID, image url, first Y coordinate, record height, number of records, number of fields, field ID, field title, help url x coordinate, pixel width, known values url. If it fails it outputs FAILED
        Parameters:
        DownloadBatchInput -
        Returns:
        DownloadBatchOutput

      • submitBatch

        public SubmitBatchOutput submitBatch(SubmitBatchInput input)
        Submits the indexed record field values for a batch to the Server. It receives and object with user's ID, password, Image ID, several field values, and several records values. It it succeeds, it outputs true. If it fails, it outputs false.

        public SearchOutput search(SearchInput input)
